    <date day="04" month="October" year="2005"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a variable length ALC PI specific LCT Header
   Extension, NTP Timestamp Header (EXT_NTP).  This extension can be
   used within an ALC session for multiple purposes, for example, to
   signal the last moment of time there was a change in the session.</t>
    </abstract>
